Package: OptiDesign
Type: Package
Title: Experimental Field Design Utilities for Optimized Layout Construction
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Félicien",
      family = "Akohoue",
      email = "akohoue.f@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Tools for constructing optimized experimental field layouts,
    including augmented, RCBD-type repeated-check designs, p-rep designs, and fixed-grid alpha row-column
    designs with repeated checks, optional grouping from family or relationship
    matrices, optional post-layout dispersion, and optional mixed-model
    efficiency diagnostics.
